text:
Your Privacy Rights Canadian Customers 
Men’s Health fitness director BJ Gaddour and Women’s Health fitness director Jen Ator kick off their New York City adventure with a killer brunch courtesy of Jack’s Wife Freda. “Is the bacon cooked in duck fat or is this duck fat bacon?” was an actual question asked. The two then check out two local gyms, including one of the biggest gyms in the city at 150,000 square feet. That’s a lot of room for burpees. Advertisement
